Interesting: Someone just deployed a contract that looks like an on-chain cleansing ritual. 
Three distinct addresses just transferred 333 tokens each to a dead wallet. Last time this pattern appeared, it was a whale preparing for a massive dump. 
Set your alerts for possible upcoming price swings.
These "ritual" transactions usually attract smart money moves.
CT might think it's a normal day, but not if you connect the dots. 
What are the odds of these wallet addresses reactivating during a full moon?
